change user password on NixOS systems that use hashedPasswordFile

USAGE: hpf-passwd [OPTIONS] [LOGIN]

ARGS:
  [LOGIN]  User to change the password of (defaults to $USER)[env: USER]

OPTIONS:
  -P, --fix-permissions  Set permissions for hashed password file without changing the file contents
      --dry-run          Show what would be done without changing any files
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
